05:38.053 --> 05:41.253
A parasite gets in, right?

05:41.285 --> 05:43.014
That's right, smart girl.

05:44.229 --> 05:48.325
Yes, the parasite
creeps into the oyster,

05:48.357 --> 05:50.245
and then the oyster responds

05:50.277 --> 05:52.518
by covering that
old, invasive little thing

05:52.548 --> 05:54.693
with this substance called nacre.

05:55.547 --> 05:58.053
And eventually, it turns

05:58.084 --> 06:01.253
what was painful and out of place

06:01.285 --> 06:03.046
into something beautiful.

06:03.077 --> 06:04.998
There is no mistake

06:05.029 --> 06:06.949
that the Bible likens
the kingdom of Heaven

06:06.980 --> 06:11.462
to a pearl of great price.

06:11.493 --> 06:14.469
And you're perfect pearls.

06:14.500 --> 06:15.557
Both of you.

06:16.773 --> 06:17.798
Thank you.

06:17.829 --> 06:19.206
Thank you.

06:19.238 --> 06:20.294
They're beautiful.

06:20.324 --> 06:23.012
Oh.

06:23.044 --> 06:25.061
Um, I gotta go.

06:26.340 --> 06:27.749
Mm, I love you.

06:34.117 --> 06:36.037
Is something off with the two of you?

06:38.852 --> 06:40.678
No, not too much.

06:40.710 --> 06:45.189
I just... I don't love her boyfriend.

06:45.220 --> 06:46.629
I know.

06:46.660 --> 06:49.157
Anybody who beeps like
that and doesn't come in

06:49.189 --> 06:50.918
can't have much to recommend him.

06:50.948 --> 06:52.005
Can he?

06:52.037 --> 06:53.797
Oh, I don't so, but...

06:55.110 --> 06:57.862
