06:57.893 --> 07:00.708
A heart wants what it wants,

07:00.741 --> 07:02.854
and it does not care.

07:02.885 --> 07:04.616
Selena Gomez?

07:05.700 --> 07:08.388
Emily Dickinson.

07:08.421 --> 07:10.277
Right.

07:13.253 --> 07:15.941
She'll figure it out. Give her time.

07:21.508 --> 07:23.526
And I want those flowers to get there

07:23.558 --> 07:25.669
bright and early tomorrow morning

07:25.700 --> 07:28.261
so that Charity knows that
we're thinking about her.

07:28.293 --> 07:30.469
Family should always be in support

07:30.500 --> 07:32.069
of those landmark moments.

07:32.102 --> 07:33.222
- Mm-hmm.
- Ooh!

07:33.252 --> 07:35.461
That's a good tweet. Hashtag...

07:35.493 --> 07:37.893
- Family first.
- I love it.

07:37.925 --> 07:39.750
- Yes. Okay.
- Yeah. Will you do that for me?

07:39.781 --> 07:41.189
Okay.

07:41.220 --> 07:43.109
Hello?

07:43.140 --> 07:44.901
I heard you're looking for me.

07:46.588 --> 07:47.733
It's Mavis.

07:49.572 --> 07:51.653
Well, I know.

07:51.684 --> 07:54.372
- I'm just surprised.
- So, what's up?

07:54.404 --> 07:57.221
<i>Well, I was going
through Mac's belongings,</i>

07:57.253 --> 08:00.102
looking for Mama's pearls
to give to the girls.

08:00.132 --> 08:01.178
Yeah?

08:01.203 --> 08:03.142
Well, I hope that's okay
with you that I did that.

08:03.174 --> 08:05.965
<i>- I separated the strands.</i>
- I don't care.

08:07.109 --> 08:09.556
The cotillion's tonight, by the way.

08:10.565 --> 08:12.684
What is this about my club?

08:13.861 --> 08:17.253
Well, Mavis, I don't pretend
to understand these things,

08:17.284 --> 08:19.441
and as you know...

08:20.005 --> 08:21.893
we don't have a lawyer since...

08:22.982 --> 08:24.403
since Mac.

08:24.436 --> 08:26.907
Mae, what is it about my club?

08:29.093 --> 08:31.578
I think you still own it.

08:45.820 --> 08:47.069
Mr. Kevin is here.

08:55.123 --> 08:57.468
What are you doing here?

08:57.500 --> 08:59.837
Looking for Charity.

08:59.869 --> 09:02.141
- She's out of town.
- Doing what?

09:02.173 --> 09:05.148
- She's touring, singing.
- And she took Nathan with her?

09:05.180 --> 09:07.645
Yes. She made arrangements for his care.

09:07.677 --> 09:09.117
She was very responsible.

09:09.149 --> 09:10.750
Now, Kevin, why are you here?

09:10.781 --> 09:12.477
I came to apologize.

09:12.508 --> 09:14.844
Oh, well, that sounds about right,

09:14.877 --> 09:16.669
given everything
that you put her through,

09:16.701 --> 09:18.333
put all of us through.

09:18.364 --> 09:19.644
I know.

09:19.676 --> 09:22.269
I'm not here to make any excuses.

09:22.300 --> 09:24.252
I was wrong to leave like that.

09:24.284 --> 09:26.780
And stay away and not respond?

09:26.813 --> 09:30.637
I know, and I'm sorry.

09:33.148 --> 09:35.709
I was having difficulty accepting

09:35.740 --> 09:37.477
who I am

09:37.917 --> 09:39.465
and what I'd done.

09:39.580 --> 09:41.277
With good reason.

09:41.309 --> 09:43.260
But I can now.

09:46.205 --> 09:48.349
I'm ready to be a father again.

09:50.493 --> 09:52.285
Where are they?

09:52.316 --> 09:54.237
You ran out of here like a little child.

09:54.269 --> 09:56.861
You don't get to march back
in here and make demands.

09:56.893 --> 09:58.750
So, I will let her know,

09:58.780 --> 10:02.206
and I'm sure she will contact
you when she's ready.

10:05.596 --> 10:08.028
He's my son,

10:08.508 --> 10:09.886
and I have rights.

10:12.476 --> 10:15.421
Well, I would love to see
you fight for them in court

10:15.452 --> 10:17.597
so that everything could be brought out

10:17.628 --> 10:21.116
about what you did to create this mess.

10:25.916 --> 10:27.613
But he's still <i> my</i> son.

10:31.452 --> 10:33.408
All right, Kevin.

10:34.333 --> 10:36.957
I will share with Charity that we spoke.

10:38.908 --> 10:42.813
Oh, and, uh, Maricel will let you out.

10:45.788 --> 10:48.637
Maricel, have them bring
Kevin's car around, please.

11:01.789 --> 11:02.910
<i> How'd it go?</i>

11:02.940 --> 11:04.253
Just like I thought it would.

11:04.285 --> 11:06.013
<i>You know I'm here for you, Kevin.</i>

11:06.045 --> 11:07.567
Yeah.

11:07.900 --> 11:09.500
I'm gonna need your help.

11:21.565 --> 11:23.133
All right, very nice.

11:23.164 --> 11:24.509
Next Greenleaf group.

11:24.540 --> 11:25.949
- Oh.
- Okay.

11:29.053 --> 11:31.518
For posterity. Wonderful!

11:31.548 --> 11:33.917
- Absolutely.
- Darius.

11:33.948 --> 11:36.413
Come on.

11:39.964 --> 11:41.500
Perfect.

11:45.340 --> 11:47.612
