- Thanks.

11:47.645 --> 11:49.180
Kind of fun, huh?

11:49.212 --> 11:52.212
Yeah, nice, clean family fun.

11:53.021 --> 11:55.580
Hey, but I got a limo for us after this.

11:55.613 --> 11:57.021
Mm, that's a no-go.

11:57.052 --> 12:00.540
What? But I got a limo.

12:00.573 --> 12:03.303
Yeah, but just for me, I mean.

12:03.335 --> 12:04.367
I can't.

12:04.397 --> 12:05.477
Why?

12:05.510 --> 12:06.590
I'll tell you later.

12:09.020 --> 12:11.923
Excellent. How about
just the grandparents?

12:14.077 --> 12:15.326
All right, darling.

12:21.660 --> 12:24.508
Let me just...
let me just focus in here.

12:26.012 --> 12:28.220
You make a public spectacle of yourself

12:28.252 --> 12:31.292
moving your clothes
50 feet down the hall,

12:31.323 --> 12:33.117
smile like nothing happened?

12:34.588 --> 12:36.220
That's right.

12:36.252 --> 12:39.242
- Unbelievable.
- Isn't it?

12:39.283 --> 12:40.691
All right, there you go.

12:40.722 --> 12:42.547
Hold it right there.

12:43.826 --> 12:45.075
All right, perfect.

12:50.962 --> 12:52.914
- Hey.
- Hey.

12:52.945 --> 12:54.674
Uh, you clocking this?

12:54.706 --> 12:56.850
- What?
- Mama and Daddy.

12:56.882 --> 12:59.826
Uh, no. Why? What's going on?

12:59.857 --> 13:02.066
He moved out of their
room into your old suite.

13:02.098 --> 13:03.922
- Is this something they do?
- Nah.

13:03.953 --> 13:06.162
I mean, they've had their
little fights over the years,

13:06.193 --> 13:08.121
but he's never moved out of the room.

13:08.817 --> 13:10.982
Do you think we should do
something about it?

13:11.697 --> 13:14.225
- I don't know what is there to do.
- Jacob.

13:14.257 --> 13:16.913
I mean, look, they're fine. It'll pass.

13:16.945 --> 13:18.355
- Hey. How are you?
- Just try to enjoy the night.

13:18.387 --> 13:20.691
All right? Have some fun.

13:22.162 --> 13:24.114
- Come on, life's too short.
- What?

13:24.147 --> 13:26.354
Mae, let it go. I don't
want to talk about it anymore.

13:26.386 --> 13:28.434
You know I have sustained...

