and Kerissa Greenleaf.

14:34.232 --> 14:36.082
Ladies and gentlemen, I present to you

14:36.114 --> 14:40.321
this year's St. Josephine
Society debutantes.

15:15.764 --> 15:17.427
Aren't they all so elegant?

15:17.458 --> 15:20.371
It is quite a show, isn't it?

15:20.403 --> 15:21.395
Mm-hmm.

15:28.786 --> 15:31.305
Like a page in <i> Southern Decor.</i>

15:31.635 --> 15:35.028
First Lady, I am so sorry

15:35.059 --> 15:37.075
about all the drama
we got into over this.

15:37.107 --> 15:39.731
Drama? What drama?

15:41.266 --> 15:42.643
Under any other circumstances,

15:42.674 --> 15:44.467
I would've never reacted the way I did.

15:47.315 --> 15:49.298
Oh, I know.

15:49.331 --> 15:52.019
I'm just so glad it all worked out.

15:52.051 --> 15:54.195
It always does.

15:54.227 --> 15:55.897
Yes.

16:48.959 --> 16:51.200
It was really good that Le'Andria

16:51.231 --> 16:53.439
could step in when
Tamela had to duck out.

16:53.471 --> 16:55.680
Yeah, yeah, these things happen.

16:55.711 --> 16:57.439
You know, if you would've
told me a year ago

16:57.471 --> 16:59.936
that this would be my life,

16:59.968 --> 17:01.248
I would've told you you were crazy.

17:01.279 --> 17:02.817
I knew it'd happen all along.

17:04.256 --> 17:06.111
- You did?
- Oh, yeah.

17:06.142 --> 17:08.480
Some people got it
and some people don't.

17:08.511 --> 17:10.528
And the ones that got it aren't
better than the ones that don't,

17:10.559 --> 17:13.343
but they've got it.

17:13.376 --> 17:14.593
And you've got it.

17:17.343 --> 17:19.263
I think you've got it, too.

17:36.959 --> 17:39.231
I'm thinking, uh, let's get the check.

17:40.831 --> 17:42.670
Me, too.

17:52.800 --> 17:54.976
Bishop, what you over here doing
hiding all by your lonesome?

17:55.007 --> 17:56.511
You should be out there cutting tile.

17:56.544 --> 17:58.591
Well, my wife's otherwise occupied.

18:01.632 --> 18:03.584
