18:06.336 --> 18:07.936
I don't think that's a good idea.

18:07.968 --> 18:09.407
Please?

18:09.439 --> 18:12.200
I was hoping for some quality time.

18:13.855 --> 18:16.412
Well, my doors at Calvary
are always open.

18:18.176 --> 18:21.375
I'm sure you know this by now, but...

18:21.727 --> 18:25.600
I'm interested in more
of a personal connection.

18:25.631 --> 18:27.327
Have been from day one.

18:28.543 --> 18:31.168
Yes, I've... I've sensed that.

18:31.199 --> 18:32.865
I've sensed that from you, too.

18:32.895 --> 18:36.127
Yes, and I'm sure that's not inaccurate,

18:36.160 --> 18:38.656
and I'm flattered, Ms. Cross.

18:38.687 --> 18:40.255
Truly, but, um...

18:40.288 --> 18:41.437
But what?

18:43.481 --> 18:45.376
Even a man of God is still a man.

18:47.776 --> 18:48.933
Ms. Cross.

18:58.847 --> 19:02.391
Hmm. I told that brother of
mine this'll never work,

19:02.424 --> 19:04.192
but he didn't want to listen.

19:04.222 --> 19:07.897
- I told him, "Basie, that old man"...
- But you know what Basie says.

19:09.090 --> 19:11.266
"There's more than one way
to skin a Greenleaf."

19:11.291 --> 19:12.860
That's right.

19:15.951 --> 19:18.960
I don't care how we do it
as long as it hurts.

19:21.018 --> 19:23.104
As long as it hurts bad.

19:23.729 --> 19:24.895
Amen.

19:24.928 --> 19:27.136
So it's one, two, three,
one, two, three.

19:27.166 --> 19:29.695
One, two, three, one, two, three.

19:29.727 --> 19:32.512
I'm gonna go get another drink.

19:36.928 --> 19:39.016
- Baby?
- Yeah?

19:39.047 --> 19:40.735
We should go ahead
and let her go out tonight.

19:40.767 --> 19:43.039
No, we talked about that.

19:43.604 --> 19:45.172
Come on, look at her.

