35:58.489 --> 36:03.098
Uh, um, just what I did was wrong.

36:03.130 --> 36:05.785
You know, I shouldn't have
put my hands on the boy.

36:05.818 --> 36:08.507
I don't know, just...

36:09.225 --> 36:10.473
